name: readyGetSet
bio: Sailing across the lands, as a true pirate does
messages: So I was looking for THEMOUSER's parents online, just was curious
Sent me into kind of a rabbit hole
There's like, no information about THEMOUSER... anywhere? Straight up, no family, no real life friends, no photos, no city, nothing.
I know they said they'd never do a face reveal, but isn't that kinda sketch?
